name: Ai fen - I like Breathing
description:
Inhale/exhale out
Everything else is just
A story you tell yourself

It is, it isn’t
It’s GONE
The moon’s light
Borrowed on borrowed time
Not MINE

Inhale/exhale out
Everything else is just
A story you tell yourself

Silence,
The true word of being
Asleep,
But we can know we’re dreaming
